if it hasn't worked by now...

06:25.818 --> 06:27.615
- Aah!
- Perhaps it's kicking in.

06:27.787 --> 06:29.118
No, I saw a mouse.

06:29.288 --> 06:31.620
- Are you sure?
- Of course, I'm sure.

06:31.791 --> 06:32.883
What'd it look like?

06:33.059 --> 06:35.619
Like Mickey,
only without the big white gloves.

06:35.795 --> 06:37.990
- Oh, my God. I see it!
- Geoffrey, get it!

06:38.164 --> 06:39.825
- Which way did it go?
That way!

06:39.999 --> 06:41.694
Thank you.

06:42.101 --> 06:43.125
No.

06:43.870 --> 06:46.065
All right. First, I'll take odds on my point.

06:46.239 --> 06:48.503
Give me a 12-dollar six and eight,
10-dollar nine.

06:48.674 --> 06:52.269
Give me five on the come, five in the field.
Keep my hard ways working for me.

06:52.445 --> 06:55.073
Oh, yeah. Split me up $10.
Boxcars and yo.

06:56.082 --> 06:59.540
And here's a buck. Spread it around.

07:00.386 --> 07:02.718
Give me them. Give me them.
Give me them.

07:03.523 --> 07:04.649
Nine. Winner.

07:04.824 --> 07:08.692
Whoo! Give me the loot. Give me the loot.
I'm a bad, bad man.

07:11.197 --> 07:15.497
All right. All right. Show me 20.
Show me 20. Show me 20.

07:15.668 --> 07:16.794
Here we go. Here we go.

07:17.370 --> 07:19.838
Oh, come on, baby. Come on, baby.

07:25.445 --> 07:28.278
Whoo-hoo-hoo! Whoo-hoo-hoo!

07:30.416 --> 07:33.146
All right, come on. It's your turn.
Roll them, C.

07:33.319 --> 07:35.685
All right, fine.

07:36.055 --> 07:37.818
Come to papa.

07:46.933 --> 07:48.833
Come on,
aren't you gonna bet something?

07:49.001 --> 07:52.061
Yes, I put $5 on red and 5 on black.

07:52.238 --> 07:54.672
That'll cancel your bet out.
You can't win like that.

07:54.841 --> 07:56.468
Maybe so, but I can't lose either.

07:56.642 --> 08:00.134
- Not unless it comes up...
Double zero, green.

08:05.518 --> 08:10.820
One penny, two penny, three...

08:10.990 --> 08:14.289
No, better not take the chance.

08:19.432 --> 08:21.127
Yes, I've got it.

08:21.300 --> 08:24.201
Hey. Hey, Carlton.
Oh, man, you are never gonna believe this.

08:24.370 --> 08:27.066
Let me tell you,
I'm at this crap table, right? It's crazy.

08:27.240 --> 08:31.176
I'm just barking numbers like, boom, seven,
boom, 11. The crowd is going crazy.

08:31.344 --> 08:35.041
The girls are like, "Willy Smith, is that you?"
I'm like, "Who you think it is?"

08:35.214 --> 08:36.977
They're going crazy. They all love me.

08:37.149 --> 08:40.208
I'm throwing back doors, yos,
Little Joes, all that kind of stuff.

08:40.385 --> 08:44.322
I'm just straight jacking the casino for their
loot. Man, I was like a crap Mandingo.

08:44.857 --> 08:47.587
- So, what happened?
- Hey, can you spot a brother 20?

08:53.933 --> 08:57.266
I cannot believe you froze me up
right in the middle of my comeback.

08:57.937 --> 09:01.600
Hi, my name is Will Smith,
and I'm a gambleholic.

09:02.174 --> 09:04.472
Carlton, come on, man.
Didn't you feel the juice?

09:04.644 --> 09:07.078
Will, that's the devil's juice.

09:07.246 --> 09:11.046
I'm about to have me
some of the devil's eggs and bacon too. Ha!

09:11.217 --> 09:13.447
Very funny, Will. Now hand it over.

09:13.619 --> 09:16.019
- What?
- You were right there when Dad said it.

09:16.188 --> 09:19.089
"Keep an eye on Will.
Make sure he doesn't get out of control.

09:19.258 --> 09:22.227
Make sure he doesn't drink
the devil's juice."

