09:31.604 --> 09:33.367
Yes.

09:38.177 --> 09:39.644
Now let's get some shuteye.

09:39.812 --> 09:42.007
Look, man, I ain't tired.

09:42.181 --> 09:45.150
Do you want to miss Hoover Dam?

09:46.786 --> 09:49.311
Hoover Dam.

09:57.964 --> 10:01.627
