10:25.091 --> 10:28.356
What am I doing? I'm gambling.
What do you think? Come on, eight.

10:28.527 --> 10:30.927
Carlton, you can't put all your money
on one number.

10:31.097 --> 10:32.587
And the winner is eight.

10:32.765 --> 10:35.734
Yes! Eight. I won.

10:35.901 --> 10:39.564
I love you, man. You know
I always loved you, man. Ha-ha-ha.

10:39.939 --> 10:41.406
Place your bets.

10:41.574 --> 10:44.737
- Hey, hey, so how much are you up?
- We're not up. We're down.

10:45.444 --> 10:46.911
What you mean "we"?

10:47.079 --> 10:49.138
Well, after I maxed out
all my credit cards...

10:49.315 --> 10:51.510
Carlton,
you maxed out all your credit cards?

10:51.684 --> 10:55.211
I had to. I couldn't get full value
for the airline tickets.

10:55.388 --> 10:56.855
You hocked our airline tickets?

10:57.023 --> 11:01.016
Well, what do you expect?
I only got $200 out of your ATM card.

11:01.193 --> 11:04.754
A word to the wise, Will,
never leave your PIN number in your wallet.

11:04.930 --> 11:07.626
You took my wallet?
Carlton, how much is left?

11:07.800 --> 11:12.328
- Whatever's left on the table.
- Wait a minute. Aah!

11:12.505 --> 11:14.336
- And the winner is eight...
- Yes!

11:14.507 --> 11:16.998
...teen.
- No!

11:20.746 --> 11:24.512
No, wait, wait. Wait a minute. It was 18,
we had eight. We should get something.

11:25.818 --> 11:30.312
What a rush. You feel that? What a ride.

11:31.023 --> 11:33.321
Carlton, you lost all our money.

11:33.492 --> 11:36.017
Oh, please.
I'm not ready to come down just yet.

11:36.629 --> 11:38.392
What the hell were you thinking, man?

11:38.564 --> 11:41.397
I was so excited about going
to Hoover Dam, I couldn't sleep.

11:41.567 --> 11:45.162
So I figured I'd come down
and place a little harmless bet and I won.

11:45.337 --> 11:48.864
You know, I tried to walk away
but the crap table just kept calling me.

11:49.041 --> 11:52.272
"Carlton. Carlton."

11:52.445 --> 11:55.710
And then the blackjack table was saying,
"You can do it."

11:55.881 --> 11:58.213
And then the slot machines
just started yelling:

11:58.384 --> 12:02.616
"Hey, you tall handsome guy,
come shake my hand."

12:02.788 --> 12:05.780
These are all my new friends.

12:05.958 --> 12:09.519
My God, they're pumping a lot of oxygen
into this room.

12:15.668 --> 12:17.329
That was the worst night of my life.

12:17.503 --> 12:20.961
Tossing and turning,
thinking about that mouse.

12:26.145 --> 12:29.672
What are you complaining about?
I'm the one who caught it and got rid of it.

12:29.849 --> 12:32.409
Mommy, Ashley's bothering me.

12:32.585 --> 12:34.553
Ashley, stop bothering your sister.

12:34.920 --> 12:37.821
- Big baby.
- She did it again.

12:37.990 --> 12:40.117
We have the whole day to ourselves
without men.

12:40.292 --> 12:44.126
- So, what are we gonna do?
- Go to the mall and scam on guys.

12:44.330 --> 12:45.888
See, Mom, she is so immature.

12:46.365 --> 12:48.458
It's Saturday, the guys are at the gym.

12:51.003 --> 12:54.666
I think the whole point of this
is for us to bond without men.

12:54.840 --> 12:57.001
- Can we talk about men?
- No.

12:57.176 --> 13:00.270
- Not even negatively?
- What you got?

13:00.446 --> 13:03.438
Okay, tell me something.
Now, are all men hard of hearing...

13:03.616 --> 13:07.245
...or is it just that they don't wanna listen
to anything we have to say?

13:07.419 --> 13:10.980
Right. We have to listen until we're blue
in the face about cars, sports...

13:11.157 --> 13:15.491
...money, their precious careers, and then
if we wanna talk about something...

13:15.661 --> 13:18.653
...that's really important to us,
they can't be bothered.

13:20.032 --> 13:23.331
Wait, how about this?
How about when they never listen? Heh.

13:29.141 --> 13:32.133
Wow, Will, the casino's head office.

13:32.311 --> 13:34.905
Can't you just feel the money?

13:35.080 --> 13:38.516
I mean, my God,
look at all the animal heads in here.

13:39.051 --> 13:42.953
Hey, Rocky,
watch me pull a rabbit out of a hat.

13:45.591 --> 13:46.922
- Shut up, Carlton.
- Ow!

13:47.092 --> 13:49.253
Now, come on,
the only way that my plan is gonna work...

13:49.428 --> 13:51.589
...is if you follow my instructions
to the letter.

13:51.764 --> 13:55.825
- Great. What are the instructions?
- "Shut the hell up."

13:59.772 --> 14:02.002
- Hello, gentlemen.
- How you doing? Will Smith.

14:02.174 --> 14:05.735
Pleasure. I understand you gentlemen
would like to discuss a little business.

14:05.911 --> 14:10.314
Heh. A little? Pshh. We got something
that is gonna rock your world.

14:10.883 --> 14:13.875
- Rock away.
- All right.

14:14.720 --> 14:16.654
Well, you know, we were talking...

14:16.822 --> 14:18.483
- Have a seat.
- Oh.

14:22.494 --> 14:25.395
We were just walking around
in your beautiful casino...

14:25.564 --> 14:29.091
...you know, fully caught up in the magic
and the fun and the excitement...

14:29.268 --> 14:32.726
