15:47.680 --> 15:50.205
Ching-ching. Huh?

15:50.382 --> 15:52.816
You can feel the electricity, can't you?
You can feel it, right?

15:52.985 --> 15:54.543
Oh, yeah. I feel it.

15:54.720 --> 15:57.587
I knew you would. You know,
I mean, there's one hitch though.

15:57.756 --> 16:00.987
I mean, we're out in the casino,
we're working our tail off for you...

16:01.160 --> 16:02.821
...and we lost all our money.

16:04.897 --> 16:06.831
Oh, so you want your money back?

16:07.299 --> 16:11.258
That is why you are you.
You deserve every one of them heads, Fred.

16:12.738 --> 16:16.469
Carlton, you taking notes from this man?
Y'all taking notes from this man?

16:16.642 --> 16:18.610
So then it's settled. Chips are fine.

16:19.178 --> 16:21.669
Uh... Is there anything else?

16:21.847 --> 16:24.509
Well, I don't know.
I wouldn't mind catching a show.

16:24.683 --> 16:28.744
- Just name it.
- Tom Jones.

16:30.189 --> 16:32.282
Who?

16:33.158 --> 16:36.525
You know what? Never mind. Never mind.
So where do we go from here?

16:36.695 --> 16:39.823
Are you gonna give it to us
or should we go out to the cashier?

16:39.999 --> 16:43.127
Basically, where we go from here
is that I'm gonna count to three...

16:43.302 --> 16:48.467
...and if you gentlemen are not out of my
office, I've got space for you on my wall.

16:54.980 --> 16:56.572
I still don't know what happened.

16:56.749 --> 17:00.048
I mean, I went into the desert
just like my father said. I had my knife.

17:00.219 --> 17:03.780
But how is a brave suppose to concentrate
with all these bells and whistles?

17:03.956 --> 17:05.617
Not to mention the keno girls.

17:05.790 --> 17:09.521
How am I gonna call my father and tell him
I'm an utter and absolute failure?

17:09.694 --> 17:12.391
I don't think it's gonna be the shock
that you think it is.

17:12.564 --> 17:15.624
Well, at least I know it's over.
The insanity is done.

17:15.800 --> 17:17.165
I'm Carlton again.

17:17.603 --> 17:21.471
- Carlton, look, a quarter.
- Oh, it's mine. It's mine.

17:23.342 --> 17:24.775
You're pathetic.

17:25.844 --> 17:27.641
You're right.

17:27.813 --> 17:29.713
I've hit rock bottom.

17:29.882 --> 17:33.181
How come you can see the quarter
and I can't?

17:33.585 --> 17:35.917
